abstract: Novak Djokovic defeats Malek Jaziri in second round of Dubai Championships; other tennis news noted.
snippet: Novak Djokovic earned his 700th career match win at the expense of the wild card Malek Jaziri, 6-1, 6-2, at the Dubai Championships in the United Arab Emirates.
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic earned his 700th career match win at the expense of the wild card Malek Jaziri, 6-1, 6-2, at the Dubai Championships in the United Arab Emirates.
